/a><a class="nav-subitem" href="#awards-talks" data-target="awards-talks"> Talks </a><a class="nav-subitem" href="#awards-press" data-target="awards-press"> Press </a> </div> </div> </nav> <div class="sidebar-footer"> <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle"> <span class="theme-icon" id="theme-sun"> <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle><path d="M12 2v2m0 16v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41m11.32 11.32l1.41 1.41M2 12h2m16 0h2M6.34 17.66l-1.41 1.41M19.07 4.93l-1.41 1.41"></path></svg> </span> <span class="theme-icon" id="theme-moon"> <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"></path><path d="M17 4l.5 1.5L19 6l-1.5.5L17 8l-.5-1.5L15 6l1.5-.5z" stroke-width="1"></path></svg> </span> </button> <div class="sidebar-credit"> <span>© 2025 Abhinav Shrivastava</span> <span>Designed with Claude Code</span> <span>Last updated Feb 2026</span> </div> </div> </aside> <main class="content"> <div class="page"> <div class="stagger">  <h1 data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko>Perception and Intelligence (PI) Lab</h1> <p class="lab-mission" data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko>We equip machines with perception abilities, enabling them to understand, interact with, and respond to their environment. We work broadly across computer vision, machine learning, and robotics.</p> <h2 class="section-anchor" id="group-current" data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko>Current Students</h2> <div class="people-grid" data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko> <div class="person"> <a href="https://ryx19th.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="person-photo"> <img src="https://ryx19th.github.io/images/1708885100870.jpeg" alt="Yixuan Ren" loading="lazy"> </a> <div class="person-name"> <a href="https://ryx19th.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yixuan Ren</a> </div> <div class="person-tag">PhD · Since 2018</div>  </div><div class="person"> <a href="http://www.cs.umd.edu/~mwalmer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="person-photo"> <img src="https://www.cs.umd.edu/~mwalmer/images/photo