hit Kambhamettu" loading="lazy"> </a> <div class="person-name"> <a href="https://architkam.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Archit Kambhamettu</a> </div> <div class="person-tag">PhD · Since 2025</div> <div class="person-coadvisor">w/ <a href="https://zcliu.cs.umd.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Prof. Leo Liu</a> </div> </div> </div> <p class="prospective-note" data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko><strong data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko>Prospective students</strong>: I am not actively looking for new PhD students beyond those I am already in touch with. That said, the broader CV group admits PhD students in computer vision, machine learning, and related fields every year. Learn more about the <a href="https://www.cs.umd.edu/grad" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko>graduate program</a> and our outstanding <a href="https://www.cs.umd.edu/research-area/computer-vision-and-machine-perception" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko>CV faculty</a>.</p> <h2 class="section-anchor" id="group-alumni" data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko>PhD Alumni</h2> <div class="alumni-list" data-astro-cid-vogdx3ko> <div class="alumni-row"> <div class="alumni-left"> <div class="alumni-name"> <a href="https://mlevy2525.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mara Levy</a> </div> <div class="alumni-thesis">From Demonstration to Dynamic Interaction: Enabling Long-Term Robotic Planning</div>   </div> <div class="alumni-right"> <div class="alumni-placement"> <span class="year">🎓 &#39;25</span> <span class="arrow">→</span><span class="company current-company">Assured Robust Intelligence (ARI)</span>  </div> </div> </div><div class="alumni-row"> <div class="alumni-left"> <div class="alumni-name"> <a href="https://shuaiyihuang.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shuaiyi Huang</a> </div> <div class="alumni-thesis">Learning Structured Alignment: From Visual Understanding to Robot Control</div>   </div> <div class="alumni-right"> <div class="alumni-placement"> <span class="ye